What you need to know:

Three-time Kenya rugby champions Mean Machine from the University of Nairobi will be away against Masinde Muliro University in Lurambi, Kakamega in one of the Kenya Rugby Union (KRU) Championship semi-final matches.The 2013 finalists Strathmore University Leos host Northern Suburbs in the other semi-final at the Leos varsity ground, Madaraka, Nairobi.